verbose_text: Western blotting results were similar to the mRNA levels, as protein levels of Wnt3a, Wnt5a, frizzled 7, disheveled 2, beta-catenin (cytoplasmic and nuclear) and LEF1 were significantly increased in the B50, B100 and Minoxidil treated groups compared with the control and B + IWR-1 groups, whereas the level of GSK3beta protein was significantly decreased in the B50, B100 and Minoxidil treated groups compared with the control and B + IWR-1 groups (XREF_FIG).
